OL,3,CPeople asked to avoid Welsh river over
OL,4,Cof 'crayfish plague' harmless to humans
OL,6,FOfficers from NRW were called to a
OL,7,Fthree-mile stretch of the river and
OL,8,Fsamples have been sent for testing,
OL,9,Fwith results expected next week. The
OL,10,Fdisease is spread by invasive non-
OL,11,Fnative crayfish.
OL,13,FNRW is asking the public to avoid
OL,14,Fentering the River Irfon to prevent
OL,15,Fthe spread of the disease, which can
OL,16,Fbe passed on through minimal contact,
OL,17,Fas a precaution.
