OL,3,CPeople asked to avoid Welsh river over
OL,4,Cof 'crayfish plague' harmless to humans
OL,6,FJenny Phillips, South Powys
OL,7,Fenvironment team leader for NRW, said:
OL,8,F"The Wye catchment, including the
OL,9,FRiver Irfon, is a key habitat for the
OL,10,Fwhite-clawed crayfish.
OL,12,F"This species is endangered, with
OL,13,Fnumbers dropping 50-80% in recent
OL,14,Fyears due to non-native crayfish and
OL,15,Fcrayfish plague.
